title: Nordo in for PA! Stump the Snob, Julius Collins, JG Join
description: We play stump the snob with Meatsauce, Zach, and Nordo. We talk about getting butts in seats once again, then chat music and Wolves with the Juice VOX Julius Collins before checking in on Dad life with Justin Gaard from Bumper to Bumper!
